                <div class="td-module-thumb"><a href="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/challenges-and-applications-of-digital-forensics/" rel="bookmark" title="Challenges and Applications of Digital Forensics"><img width="180" height="135" class="entry-thumb" src="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/digital-forensics-180x135.png" srcset="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/digital-forensics-180x135.png 180w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/digital-forensics-80x60.png 80w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/digital-forensics-100x75.png 100w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/digital-forensics-238x178.png 238w" sizes="(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px" alt="digital forensics, cyber forensics, forensics" title="Challenges and Applications of Digital Forensics"/></a></div>                            </div>

            <div class="item-details">
                <h3 class="entry-title td-module-title"><a href="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/challenges-and-applications-of-digital-forensics/" rel="bookmark" title="Challenges and Applications of Digital Forensics">Challenges and Applications of Digital Forensics</a></h3>            </div>
        </div>
        </div><div class="td-mega-span">
        <div class="td_module_mega_menu td_mod_mega_menu">
            <div class="td-module-image">
                <div class="td-module-thumb"><a href="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/skills-gap-new-approach-strong-cybersecurity-teams/" rel="bookmark" title="Why Skills Gap is an Opportunity for a New Approach to Building Strong Cybersecurity Teams"><img width="180" height="135" class="entry-thumb" src="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-180x135.jpg" srcset="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-180x135.jpg 180w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-80x60.jpg 80w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-100x75.jpg 100w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-238x178.jpg 238w, https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/MicrosoftTeams-image-8-853x640.jpg 853w" sizes="(max-width: 180px) 100vw, 180px" alt="security, teams, skills" title="Why Skills Gap is an Opportunity for a New Approach to Building Strong Cybersecurity Teams"/></a></div>                            </div>

            <div class="item-details">
                <h3 class="entry-title td-module-title"><a href="https://cisomag.eccouncil.org/skills-gap-new-approach-strong-cybersecurity-teams/" rel="bookmark" title="Why Skills Gap is an Opportunity for a New Approach to Building Strong Cybersecurity Teams">Why Skills Gap is an Opportunity for a New Approach to Building Strong Cybersecurity Teams</a></h3>            </div>
